# =====================================================================
# AF is publish-safe after excluding the items below.
#
# The model REPORTS (earth/glmnet/mgcv *.html) and PLOTS are KEPT/publishable:
# verified free of addresses, MLS/transaction IDs, and parcel IDs. They contain
# only aggregate model output (coefficients, equations, fit stats, effect
# plots). Note: equations expose latitude/longitude *knot values* (region-level
# aggregate, ~34.749) — not property-level data.
# =====================================================================

# macOS / scratch / Office lock files
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
~$*
**/~$*
Comparative

# --- Confidential / oversized: never commit --------------------------
# Spreadsheets = comp-level MLS data (addresses, parcel/MLS IDs, prices)
*.xlsx
# RDS: the 477 MB earth result exceeds GitHub's 100 MB limit and stores the
# raw x/y matrix; the report_data bundles are build artifacts not needed for
# display. (Reports are self-contained HTML, so no rds is required to view.)
*.rds
